of this mars ship using the space shuttle to <br>
55,000,000,000 Dollars for one vessel. <br>
18. If we use Zubrins approach, and send a 1 way return<br>
unmanned earth return vehicle, then send a 1 way <br>
manned mission from leo . It will costs less because the rquired ships would be smaller in mass due to their lower mass ratio requirements for the mars mission .<br>
.19. For a 1 way mars shot we need just two two 3/1 mass ratio 450 second  H2 + O2  stages, and  not three in leo for this  mission.<br>
20. The price tag is why congress refused to fund this sort<br>
of thing in the past.<br>
21. The price results from the chemical drive mars ships<br>
overall mass ratio requirement of 55/1 for the mission<br>
starting from leo.<br>
